  <p class="mb-8">Getting people's attention is EXPENSIVE, especially when targeting demographics, yet tribes are always listening to hear your brand voice and want to connect to your product.</p>

  <h2 class="secondary--text mb-2">Sales become effortless.</h2>
  <p class="mb-8">Convincing people to change is HARD, habits can be real hurdles, but your tribe is ready for change and wanting you to help them reach their goals.</p>

  <h2 class="secondary--text mb-2">Innovation is safe.</h2>
  <p class="mb-8">Making changes to a product is TRICKY, and more can go wrong than right, yet your tribe feels compelled to share their thoughts, try new things, and help you to make great products.</p>

